{"id": 2590, "genre": 1001, "title": "【CHANEL嘉柏丽尔香水】你最不想要被磨平的棱角是什么？", "description": "不管怎么说都想要真性情一回的冲动呀！", "record_count": 13553, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181103192219qjSAacROY526BirI.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 310020, "content": "不轻易听信旁人所谓的人生经验，比如什么:本来就该 理所当然 不可能 就挺好 别傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476290}, {"id": 309005, "content": "尽力坦荡 永远正直", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494663}, {"id": 309007, "content": "自己思考过的经不起推敲的从众心理做出的行为", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 309011, "content": "我说不要就不要", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494706}, {"id": 309012, "content": "想要冲破之前为自己设下的条条框框，真正去发掘属于自己的东西，多关注自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494709}, {"id": 309013, "content": "冲破之前为自己设下的条条框框，去发掘真正属于自己的东西，并且多关注自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494709}, {"id": 311834, "content": "自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467927}, {"id": 309290, "content": "😂😂😂", "image": "img/option/option/20181107174350TN5AbMRV8soPU0gp", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1162505}, {"id": 308781, "content": "吃火锅一定只点辣锅，蘸干碟不要水，点鸳鸯的都是纸老虎", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 308782, "content": "即使在快节奏的社会也不做无用社交狗，多用时间来丰满自己的灵魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3972, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 308783, "content": "在生活中，像如懿一样能够坚守最善良的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 507, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 308784, "content": "现在都说娱乐至上，却依然想要严肃看待每一起发生在自己身上的事件", "image": null, "praise_count": 1349, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 310837, "content": "开心与不开心 我TM都想大声的表达出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502996}, {"id": 308792, "content": "公司聚会，别想让我站起来嘻嘻哈哈热场子，你给的钱还不够呢。一个饭局5万，我能把你喝死如果你需要 还能陪睡。（安静的微笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 882, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 308794, "content": "媳妇可以不漂亮，但是一定要和我一样有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379987}, {"id": 309050, "content": "那么在意别人的话干嘛呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154871}, {"id": 309306, "content": "随心的拒绝与不附和", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496156}, {"id": 308795, "content": "火锅我想怎么吃就怎么吃，你管我全辣还是鸳鸯，你长得丑 我还没说你，你管我怎么吃？", "image": null, "praise_count": 458, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 308796, "content": "做自己，喜欢的有思想的音乐、电影，保持自己的一些思考，可能会很孤独，但是一个人欣赏、思考不也挺好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1545, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352811}, {"id": 308797, "content": "忙也绝不点外卖！一定要堂吃！生活仪式感", "image": null, "praise_count": 461, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230166}, {"id": 308798, "content": "真性情不是冲动，是勇气和一种原则。", "image": null, "praise_count": 711, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493509}, {"id": 308799, "content": "好好的丰富自己呀 有趣的事情那么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492716}, {"id": 308800, "content": "带着自尊爱一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 731, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800043}, {"id": 309312, "content": "人生应该有很多面，不想千篇一律，也不想千人一面，只想做自己，属于我的每一面都不该被磨平", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496169}, {"id": 309313, "content": "不想委屈求全，生活已经如此的艰难，坚持自己的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496171}, {"id": 308802, "content": "我没用过这款香水", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430930}, {"id": 309314, "content": "发火明明很多时候是有用的，\n为什么要忍着当个老好人？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075659}, {"id": 309059, "content": "永远心存梦想\n永远热泪盈眶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150589}, {"id": 309315, "content": "外圆内方，乃做人最好的处事态度，就像#香奈儿嘉柏丽儿香水#一样有棱有角，独具光芒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496175}, {"id": 309316, "content": "童心鸭！都告诉我成年人要理智！要努力！要强大！可是有时候真的会好累😔想要保留一点简单的傻傻的快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496181}, {"id": 308805, "content": "坚持自我啊 像如懿一样 不论周围如何变 始终坚持自己的初心 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493555}, {"id": 308806, "content": "坚持真我，坚持初心", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203403}, {"id": 308807, "content": "讨厌附和别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066696}, {"id": 308808, "content": "欢乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470479}, {"id": 308809, "content": "不想谄媚，讨厌推诿", "image": null, "praise_count": 811, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493563}, {"id": 308810, "content": "学校的校级学生组织，那些垃圾风气老子一辈子都不会屌……", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484333}, {"id": 312138, "content": "早睡早起，爱吃蔬菜，坚持锻炼，从不迟到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465338}, {"id": 308811, "content": "敢怒敢言 敢笑敢哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470479}, {"id": 308812, "content": "勇敢对丑的事物say no", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 308813, "content": "坚持自己喜欢的电影，书，综艺，电视剧……坚决不看脑残片脑残电视剧，不管有多少人推荐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250762}, {"id": 308814, "content": "就算看周围的马屁精混的风生水起，但我死也无法，挥下我的手。", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493577}, {"id": 308816, "content": "再忙也要留时间喝茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453267}, {"id": 314192, "content": "生活的仪式感", "image": "img/option/option/20181202101136J93mlTOGPfArS07R", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520779}, {"id": 315728, "content": "坚持那种我所认为的野生，即便所有人都觉得我的眉毛画的很难看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516921}, {"id": 309329, "content": "拥有自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486932}, {"id": 308819, "content": "不喜欢在工作的时候插科打诨、嘻嘻哈哈，认真工作早点回家！", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 308821, "content": "不在意他人的眼光，做自己的自己。哪怕不合群，也能坚持自己的观点和选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476960}, {"id": 308823, "content": "精神独立，思想自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 308824, "content": "丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160463}, {"id": 308825, "content": "不想结婚就不结，一个人单着快乐，不被中国结婚生子的传统幸福观束缚", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467141}]}